    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving, naturally aspirated engineering. The S54B32 power plant features a fully overhauled VANOS system and documented rod bearing replacement, ensuring the 8,000 RPM redline remains reliable. Power is transmitted via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual to a reinforced rear subframe, mitigating the chassis fatigue common to this platform. The suspension geometry remains factory-spec with fresh bushings, while the limited-slip differential provides optimal lock-up. Presented in showroom condition with original paint depth and a pristine interior, this vehicle offers the razor-sharp throttle response and tactile feedback that defined an era of performance motoring.",
